        public RatingVector getUserRatingVector(int userId)
        Description copied from interface: Provider
        Getting a rating vector (a vector of ratings) of specified user. Note, rating vector represented RatingVector contains ratings. If rating vector is user rating vector, it contains all ratings of the same user on many items. If rating vector is item rating vector, it contains all ratings of many users on the same item.

      • createSchema

        public boolean createSchema(AttributeList userAttList,
                            AttributeList itemAttList)
        Description copied from interface: Provider
        Each database has a schema as the structure of such database. This method re-create the framework database by importing the other schema specified by given user attribute list and item attribute list. Note, provider allows programmers to access all data objects stored in archives (files) of entire framework. These data objects constitute framework database including user profile, item profile, rating matrix, context template, context, etc. Such database has the schema.
        Specified by:
        createSchema in interface Provider
        Overrides:
        createSchema in class ProviderImpl
        Parameters:

        whether create schema successfully.
